{"tid":1008138,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"\"高敏感人\"圍爐取暖","createTime":"2019-02-04T09:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T09:33:30.000Z","uid":87518,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2c66d0377bdbb78b09402e5885a63fa994c65a","tid":1008138,"uid":87518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"其實係想睇下連登有幾多哩種人<br />\n早兩日去圖書館，咁啱睇到 <br />\n《高敏感是種天賦》/ Highly Sensitive People，原來自己嘅性格係好多人都有，重有一個詞去形容。以下係從書中quote 高敏感人常見嘅特質 <br />\n1. 可同時吸收多項資訊<br />\n2. 能辨識聲音或氣味的細微差別 （如果環境有東西突然改變，會嚇一大跳）<br />\n3. 能緩慢、深入且多元地思考<br />\n4. 行事謹慎，危機處理能力強<br />\n5. 具有高度的同理心，很替人著想 <br />\n6. 誠實，有責任感<br />\n7. 想像力豐富的精神生活<br />\n8. 因為自尊心低落，所以得更「優秀」 <br />\n9. 以為自己不努力，別人就不會喜歡自己 <br />\n10. 很喜歡獨處，可以一直思考事情（很受身邊環境影響，對身邊聲音，氣氛很敏感）<br />\n<br />\n書中講到哩種人好容易畀人感覺係內向，或者有人嚴重到會覺得自己有自閉症傾向，<br />\n可能有人會覺得咁樣去分析或者將人分類有啲似星座嗰啲，但係我本人係中咗九成，有相同特質嘅巴打可以上網睇下相關嘅資料。<br />\nYou are not alone."},{"pid":"36438c361ffb61774acfabf105ab7ea9b62f4e2d","tid":1008138,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Vmdtxk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Vmdtxk.png&h=5c9eef5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0b0161f00c9bb456faca0d59756c79e97a861","tid":1008138,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf5c9d3d6ccef884bce30787bdda6bef6699fd4","tid":1008138,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 